title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Boudreau/Myers/Florio/Foligno/Russo
description:
Live from the Xcel, head coach Bruce Boudreau in first thing this morning, recovering from yet another loss. Dan Myers and his Vox record. It was Nordo vs Dubnyk on the court. Being attacked by Stalock in the box. Mike Florio checks in with breaking news. 
Winger, Marcus Foligno talks movies and babies with PA, and then they bury the hatchet. Turning Nordo's frown upside down and Russo from the road.
